com.facebook.litho.sections

Class ChangeSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.sections.ChangeSet

  • public final class ChangeSet
extends java.lang.Object
    A ChangeSet represent a list of Change that has to be applied to a SectionTree.Target as the result of an update of a Section. A ChangeSet is provided in the OnDiff of a DiffSectionSpec to allow the ChangeSetSpec to define its changes based on old/new props and state.
